Stack<T> - Class in src.StackADT
An implementation of the StackInterface interface to create Stacks using a resizeable list We have variable for the list itself which is created using a LIFO (Last In First Out) approach The three methods for a stack are Push, Peek, and Pop, but there are also various methods like clear and isEmpty.
